[These results from the Imperial College modelling are helpful in presenting a justification for suspecting the number of cases currently occurring in Wuhan City is greater than the number officially confirmed. One has to remember that while mild cases may have been detected in the official investigation surrounding the outbreak associated with the Huanan Wholesale Seafood Market, which involved active case surveillance, milder cases occurring in the community not directly associated with contact with the seafood market or with individuals involved in the seafood market cluster might well not come to the attention of the health sector and therefore would not be included in identified cases. This is a newly identified virus causing a febrile respiratory disease associated with pneumonia (but percentage of infected individuals presenting with pneumonia is not currently known). There is much to be learned, in spite of recognizing much has already been learned in a very short time. - Mod.MPP]
